<% content_for :title, "License badge — Printwright" %>
<div class="container" style="max-width: 720px">
  <h1>Embed your license badge</h1>
  <p>Every license gets an embeddable badge that links to its live on-chain check.
    Put it on your product page, your shop listing, anywhere — a buyer one click away
    from public proof beats a claim.</p>

  <p><img src="<%= verify_badge_path(cert_id: "pw-000001", format: :svg) %>" alt="example Printwright license badge" width="200" height="36"></p>

  <h2>Snippet</h2>
  <p class="t-small muted">Replace <code>pw-000001</code> with your certificate id (it's on your receipt and the verify page).</p>
  <pre class="mono t-small" style="overflow-x:auto"><code>&lt;a href="<%= verify_url("pw-000001") %>"&gt;
  &lt;img src="<%= verify_badge_url("pw-000001", format: :svg) %>"
       alt="Printwright licensed unit pw-000001" width="200" height="36"&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>What it proves</h2>
  <p class="t-small">The badge itself proves nothing — the page it links to does: a live,
    field-by-field comparison against the public Hedera mirror node. A printable
    certificate is available from the same page.</p>

  <h2>Independent verification widget</h2>
  <p class="t-small">For proof that does not depend on this marketplace, add the standalone
    widget to any HTML page. It reads the named Hedera mirror topic directly, validates the
    frozen PWC-1 fields, and links to the exact consensus message. Replace both identifiers
    with the values on your receipt.</p>
  <pre class="mono t-small code-block"><code>&lt;script defer src="<%= request.base_url %>/printwright-verify-widget.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;printwright-verify cert-id="pw-000058"
  topic-id="0.0.9585069" network="testnet"&gt;
&lt;/printwright-verify&gt;</code></pre>
  <p class="t-small"><%= link_to "Open the plain HTML example", "/widget-example.html" %>.</p>
</div>
